These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, reading
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, orange, light-blue
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, tiparillo, game
1. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the game-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who likes light-blue is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking   | reading   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| Color   | light-blue  | grey    | orange      |
| Cigar     | tiparillo     | blend      | game |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, skateboard, train
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, april, june
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person driving the train##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person eating kale is the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the person driving the skateboard and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Transport   | skateboard     | train     | car      |
| Birthday   | june  | april | july |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | frog     | goat       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, orange
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, azalea, begonia
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
3 different games are played: chess, whist, domino
1. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person playing chess is between the person who growsbegonia and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
4. the person playing whist is the person eating kale##1
5. the person playing chess is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Food          | eggplant  | orange     | kale     |
| Flower           | begonia | tulip  | azalea   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| Game           | domino     | chess | whist |

