.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, canadian, thai
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, scientist
3 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, guinea-pig
House: futuristic, modern, cottage
1. the futuristic house is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the thai is between the paramedic and the owner of the cat##2
4. the canadian is the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Nationality    | colombian       | thai  | canadian   |
| Job     | paramedic    | scientist  | journalist |
| Pet     | chinchilla   | guinea-pig | cat        |
| House   | cottage | futuristic     | modern      |

