3 different games are played: snooker, whist, chess
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, country, d&b
3 different pets are kept: fish, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is the person playing snooker##1
3. the fan of country is between the person who's birthday is in march and the owner of the horse##2
4. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Birthday          | march | july | february    |
| Game         | whist | chess      | snooker |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | country     | d&b        |
| Pet           | fish      | mouse       | horse      |

