.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, funk, dubstep
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, dancer, nurse
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, western
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, van
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the dancer is between the fan of dubstep and the person driving the car##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
5. the dancer is between the nurse and the person watching comedy movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Music-Genre          | dubstep      | funk   | pop |
| Job         | scientist | dancer | nurse |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy      | western | fantasy   |
| Transport     | van         | roller  | car       |

