1. the journalist is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the architect is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person driving the bike##2
5. the person driving the trike is the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Transport      | subway       | trike      | bike      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | chinchilla-climbing | chess      |
| Job           | journalist | architect     | dressmaker |
| Pet   | bird     | chinchilla          | hedgehog       |

