3. the owner of the fish is the person eating cucumber##1
4. the owner of the lizard is the social-worker##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the engineer##1
6. the person driving the roller is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
