2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the australian is on the left of the spanish##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the owner of the ferret and the person who's birthday is in april##2
6. the person who's birthday is in july is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | iced-tea      | tea            |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard | ferret |
| Birthday   | april     | december        | july         |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | australian    | spanish        |

