3. the police-officer is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the fan of disco##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the fan of trance##1
6. the coach is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
