3. the tower house is the person eating avocado##1
4. the person eating broccoli is the cape-cod house##1
5. the person driving the airplane is the person eating garlic##1
6. the egyptian is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
