2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the fan of disco is between the craftsman house and the person who growsaconite##2
4. the fan of reggae is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is between the art-deco house and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
